<p>Number of saved cities: <b><?=$city_count?></b></p>
<p>Number of ecards sent: <b><?=$card_count?></b></p>
<p>Number of votes cast: <b><?=$vote_count?></b></p>
<p>Number of cities in gallery: <b><?=$gall_count?></b></p>
